Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.72,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}I won't forget the promise we made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.01,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,0)}I'll close my eyes and make sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:50.02,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}Shaking off the darkness that closed in on me, I continue to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:05.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}When can I see once more the future that I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:11.96,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}Again and again, I'll tear apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:16.75,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}...the shadow of distress that spilled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:22.01,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}...and walk on in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:27.60,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}The time that ticked away...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:33.23,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}...ceaselessly now announces the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.57,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}Putting my unchanging feelings into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:43.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,0)}I'll open the closed door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:49.70,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,250)}My heart awoke to draw the future where I'd start running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:54.83,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}Even if I come to a standstill on a difficult road,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:04:01.84,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,250)}the sky is always waiting for me in a beautiful blue, so I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:07.97,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(250,0)}By now, no matter what happens, I won't get broken.
