Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You deceived us, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely asked if you wanted to be a magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't explain some aspects of being one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you never found out, it wouldn't have bothered you a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami, for example, never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you humans don't even realise you have souls in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:01:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body's nothing more than a collection of neurons and a centralised cardiovascular system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when a human body can no longer maintain life, its soul vanishes along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave your soul a physical form to prevent that from happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, a form you can pick up with your own hands and protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way you can battle witches a little more safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking combat far too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, how much do you think it would stimulate your...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pain receptors if your stomach were to be impaled by a spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it would actually feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even move, and that's how it would feel with only one strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason you were able to remain standing during...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your fight with Kyouko was that anything too painful was limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only possible because your\Nconsciousness isn't directly linked with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You survived your fight because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got used to it, you could learn to completely cut off all pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since your reaction times would slow, I don't suggest it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a wish so important that you\Nagreed to a fate of combat, am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your wish came true, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan, did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has believed me thus far,\Neven when I warned them in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Kyubey do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't think it's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a creature that doesn't understand human values.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just say it was an appropriate\Npayment for bringing about a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did that to her, and all Sayaka-chan\Nwanted to do was heal someone she loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was still a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made the impossible possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Miki Sayaka spent her entire life tending to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would never have been able to play the violin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally a miracle costs far more than a human life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Kyubey goes around selling them for that price.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan won't be able to go back to her normal life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said this already, have I not? Give up on Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sayaka-chan wasn't a magical girl at the time, Hitomi-chan and I would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't confuse gratitude and responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way for you to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to repay her so you don't feel inferior,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not your place and you need to stop thinking that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan, why are you always so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I am. It might be because I'm no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I visit Kyousuke after being turned into this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how long are you going to lay there and mope, dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beginning to regret what was done to your body, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of just going with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can do whatever I want with the power I got out of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really something to regret at the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got what you deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea. You can think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you live only for yourself, everything you do is your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no reason to resent others, and there's no way you'll have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get through just about anything if you think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be kind of a long talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my dad's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was extremely honest and way too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day when he read the newspaper in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd start to tear up and seriously worry about things. He was that type of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad always said that in order to save a new era, you'd need a new type of religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why sometimes he'd preach things that weren't part of the doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, everyone stopped coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was even excommunicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would listen to what he had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem like some sort of sketchy cult if you knew nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wouldn't matter if he was talking about doing what was right,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or what was obvious, he was an outcast in the eyes of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our whole family was left with nothing, not even food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad wasn't saying anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just saying things that differed from the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone would lend him their ear for just five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd realise that what he was saying was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one listened to him in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear the fact that no one understood what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked Kyubey to make it so people would seriously listen to what he was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning, my dad's church was filled with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of believers multiplied at a frightening rate each day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I became yet another magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how good my dad's sermons were, it wouldn't help in killing any of the witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was where I came in, so I got all hyped up about it like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that my dad and I would save the world. He publicly, and I from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day my dad found out what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad completely flipped out once he found out most of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...followers were there not because of his sermons, but because of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called me, his daughter, a witch that swayed people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty funny, huh? I had been fighting real witches every night and that's what he had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then my dad snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was pitiful in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drowned himself in alcohol and went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually he took his whole family with him and killed himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish destroyed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ended up worse off just because I made a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...selfish wish without knowing what anyone else would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:12:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I swore to myself that I'd never use magic for others again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd use my powers only for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles aren't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for hope, an equal amount of despair scatters across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all cancels out to zero. That's how the balance of the world is maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to stop worrying about everything and do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, since you got what you deserve becoming a magical girl and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to live only for yourself, why did you even worry about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both started from the same mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't continue regretting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already paid too much for what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should start thinking about how to get some change back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to realise that, but you keep making mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just hard to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the wrong idea about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for that. I apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't regret the fact that I used my wish for someone else's benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to never regret my actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't cheapen the feelings I had when I first made the wish. Not now, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that I've paid too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do plenty of wonderful things with this power, depending on how I use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you? How did you get those apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get the money to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say anything, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat one of those apples, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't even want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're magical girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one else like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue to fight in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens to conflict with you in some way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can just try to kill me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose, and I won't hate you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a little sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, Kamijou-kun was released from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou, are you OK now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If I sit at home all day, my rehabilitation won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aiming for being able to walk without crutches by next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Kamijou-kun's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, go say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't said anything to him yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you about someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been keeping something from you and Madoka-san for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...been attracted to Kamijou Kyousuke-kun for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have expected that from you, Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke's pretty suave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've known him for a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we just kinda hang out because we've known each other for a while, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I won't lie to myself any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-san, can you come to terms with your own feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want to try and go after him if you're already with him, or try to steal him from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've spent far more time with him than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should have the right to go after him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell Kamijou-kun after school tomorrow that I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait one day exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please decide on a course of action that you won't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you whether or not you think you should tell him how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to be alone, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so kind to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I almost started to regret what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, just for one second, about what would have happened if I didn't save Hitomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure of a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't look Mami-san in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi is going to take Kyousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask him to hold me when I've become this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask him to kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go. We have to get us a witch tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you're just sitting here watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fighting a witch today, not a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll drop a Grief Seed. It's not a pointless hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'd let her take your prey for that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn, I couldn't just sit there any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you really don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have to feel pain any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.16,0:24:00.20,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a different type of magical girl than all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:02.08,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.81,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any reward for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:08.17,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never use magic for my own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:11.01,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really stupid.
